<task id="task-6669" class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">Use bearer authentication in <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/></title><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><context class="- topic/section task/context ">To use the bearer authentication in Katalon Studio, do as follows:</context><steps class="- topic/ol task/steps "><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Open a web service test object, then navigate to the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Authorization</uicontrol> tab.</cmd></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the dropdown list of <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Type</uicontrol>, choose <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Bearer</uicontrol>.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="700" href="ks-840-authorization-type.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">Authorization dropdown list</alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Enter your bearer token.</cmd><info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info "><image width="700" href="ks-840-add-token.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">add bearer token</alt></image></info></step><step class="- topic/li task/step "><cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">To use this bearer authentication, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Update to HTTP Header</uicontrol>.</cmd></step></steps><result class="- topic/section task/result ">The bearer token is added to the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">HTTP Header</uicontrol> with the value as <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph ">Bearer &lt;myBearerToken&gt;</codeph>.<p class="- topic/p "><image width="700" href="ks-840-http-header.png" class="- topic/image "><alt class="- topic/alt ">bearer token in HTTP header</alt></image></p></result></taskbody></task>